Hi, welcome to the item spreadsheet for ACNH!

Update 10/13: Added "Kit Type" column to furniture for the type of item used to customise furniture. Added three new columns to clothing tabs, "Gender", "Villager Gender", and "Seasonality", which all influence how NPCs interact with the item. Fixed some values for the 1.5.0 items and updated some museum phrases.

Update 09/30: Halloween items are here! Added all new recipes and items from 1.5.0 with associated data, added new Reactions, added Jack to Special NPC tab. Added `Default Umbrella` column to Villagers tab. Added `Inventory Filename` and `Storage Filename` columns to Other tab. Minor fixes to various source notes, DIY sell prices, and other minor fixes. Deleted `Version Unlocked` column.

Please join the Discord server if you are a developer and need a more in-depth changelog.

The purpose of our spreadsheet is to create a complete collection of data on items, villagers, achievements, and more! We fully welcome the use of our data for creators to make websites or applications from for the betterment of the Animal Crossing community. If you use our data for an app or site, please provide a link back to the spreadsheet on your page, and contact us to get your name added to the list of partners.
